Localization.Name: Quartz "Crusader" Energy SMG
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: Verified Offworld Laser Technologies
Item Type: SMG
Class: Energy (Electron)

Battery Size: 45
Rate of Fire: Beam
Effective Range: 15-20 m

Attachments: Optics (S1), Underbarrel (S1)

Manufacturer VOLT's Quartz SMG utilizes exciting new weapon technology that fires a short range beam that fractures into multiple beams the longer it fires, making it an extremely effective close quarter weapon. This special edition features Crusader branding.
